So that's the manager's job.

71
00:06:02,139 --> 00:06:04,206
You acknowledge that I am the manager's role.

72
00:06:04,464 --> 00:06:05,668
I tell you then.

73
00:06:07,322 --> 00:06:10,558
You have a lot of motivation!Alright, I'll go with you.

