I am his manager.....

96
00:07:34,503 --> 00:07:39,028
There’s a boring violent incident from the past, and there’s a trial coming up soon

97
00:07:39,762 --> 00:07:42,012
Well, going to prison is tough,

98
00:07:43,145 --> 00:07:46,309
