Men these days are very difficult.

120
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,326
so I'm waiting outside for a bit

121
00:09:30,317 --> 00:09:34,036
Kamoi-san,
I move by shaking my body like this.

122
00:09:34,099 --> 00:09:34,895
You are stupid.

123
