166
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,958
Just having you around is a burden

167
00:11:46,637 --> 00:11:48,215
please go away

168
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:50,669
You are very heartless.

169
00:11:52,596 --> 00:11:54,028
Please leave

170
