196
00:13:32,217 --> 00:13:34,067
That's tough

197
00:13:35,091 --> 00:13:37,458
but You know what?

198
00:13:38,070 --> 00:13:41,254
If you want a handsome child, just imagine my face.

199
00:13:41,411 --> 00:13:44,958
It's ridiculous, but my partner is my partner,

200
