Kamoi brought Miyamoto Yumi with him.

249
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,919
He apparently wants to meet her sister.

250
00:18:17,919 --> 00:18:18,849
Emi?

251
00:18:19,981 --> 00:18:20,996
Emi

